              How is the frequency of <em>this</em>
              note related to the one from part (a)?
              Draw a sketch of the standing wave to support your answer.
            </p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </p>
    </statement>
  </exercise>
  <exercise xml:id="prob_OrganPipes">
